#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdiskfree; displays the available file devices (hard drive partitions, "
"floppy and &CD; drives, USB sticks &etc;) along with information on their "
"capacity, free space, type and mount point. It also allows you to mount and "
"unmount drives and view them in a file manager."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; prikazuje dostupne datotečne uređaje (particije hard diska, "
"diskete i &CD; jedinica, USB stikovi &etc;) zajedno sa informacijama o "
"njihovom kapacitetu, slobodnom prostoru, tipu i tački priključenja. Također "
"vam dopušta da montirate i demontirate jedinice i pogledate ih u fajl "
"menadžeru."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kdiskfree; is similar to the &kinfocenter; Partitions module, but takes "
#| "up less screen space. It is useful if you want to keep a &kdiskfree; "
#| "window available at all times."
msgid ""
"&kdiskfree; is similar to the &systemsettings; Storage Devices module, but "
"takes up less screen space. It is useful if you want to keep a &kdiskfree; "
"window available at all times."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; je sličan &kinfocenter; modulu particija, ali zauzima manje "
"prostora na ekranu. Korisan je ukoliko želite čuvati &kdiskfree; prozor "
"dostupan sve vrijeme."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "Korištenje &kdiskfree;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "Pokretanje &kdiskfree;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Type <userinput><command>kdf</command></userinput> at a command prompt or "
#| "select <guimenuitem>Disk Free</guimenuitem> from the <guisubmenu>System</"
#| "guisubmenu> group in the application launcher. The standard &Qt; and "
#| "&kde; command options are available, and can be listed by entering "
#| "<userinput><command>kdf</command> <option>--help</option></userinput> at "
#| "the command prompt."
msgid ""
"Type <userinput><command>kdf</command></userinput> at a command prompt or "
"select <guimenuitem>KDiskFree</guimenuitem> from the <guisubmenu>System</"
"guisubmenu> group in the application launcher. The standard &Qt; and &kde; "
"command options are available, and can be listed by entering "
"<userinput><command>kdf</command> <option>--help</option></userinput> at the "
"command prompt."
msgstr ""
"Unesite <userinput><command>kdf</command></userinput> u command promptu ili "
"odaberite <guimenuitem>Disk Free</guimenuitem> iz <guisubmenu>System</"
"guisubmenu> grupe pri pokretanju aplikacije. Standardne &Qt; i &kde; "
"mogućnosti naredbi su dostupne, i mogu biti izlistane unosom "
"<userinput><command>kdf</command> <option>--help</option></userinput> u "
"command prompt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To run the application as an applet in the systemtray, use "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>KwikDisk</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in application launcher."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The features of &kdiskfree; are also available in the &systemsettings; "
"module <guilabel>Storage Devices</guilabel>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main window"
msgstr "Glavni prozor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main &kdiskfree; window displays the available file devices."
msgstr "Glavni &kdiskfree; prozor prikazuje dostupne datotečne uređaje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normally, the following pieces of information are included:"
msgstr "Normalno, uključene su sljedeće informacije:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kdiskfree; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kdiskfree; Ekran</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kdiskfree; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kdiskfree; Ekran</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "an icon depicting the type of storage"
msgstr "ikonica prikazuje vrstu mjesta za pohranu podataka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "device name"
msgstr "naziv uređaja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "filesystem type"
msgstr "tip datotečnog sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "total size"
msgstr "ukupna veličina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "mount point"
msgstr "tačka priključenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "free disk space"
msgstr "slobodni prostor na disku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "the percentage of space used as a number and as a graph."
msgstr "postotak iskorištenog prostora izraženo brojčano i grafikonom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> clicking on the header of a particular "
"column sorts the devices according to that variable. A second "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click sorts in the opposite order."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Lijevi</mousebutton> klik na header određene kolone sortira "
"uređaje prema toj varijabli. Drugi <mousebutton>lijevi</mousebutton> klik ih "
"sortira u suprotnom poretku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &RMB; on a row pops up a menu. If that device is not "
"currently mounted, the <guimenuitem>Mount Device</guimenuitem> option is "
"available. If the device is mounted, it can be unmounted by choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Unmount Device</guimenuitem>. Selecting <guimenuitem>Open in "
"File Manager</guimenuitem> opens a new window with a graphical view of the "
"files on that device."
msgstr ""
"Klikom sa &RMB; na red iskače meni. Ukoliko taj uređaj nije trenutno "
"montiran, <guimenuitem>Montiraj Uređaj</guimenuitem> opcija je dostupna. Ako "
"je uređaj montiran, može biti demontiraj odabirom <guimenuitem>Demontiraj "
"Uređaj</guimenuitem>. Odabirom <guimenuitem>Otvori u Fajl Manadžeru</"
"guimenuitem> otvra se novi prozor sa grafičkim pregledom datoteka na tom "
"uređaju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The setting for the file manager used by &kdiskfree; is independent from the "
"choice in the &systemsettings; module <guilabel>Default Applications</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Bar and Configuration"
msgstr "Meni bar i Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
