"Postavke</ulink> i <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui.html#menus-help\">Meni "
"Pomoć</ulink> osnova &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Postavke Dijaloga"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure &kdiskfree; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Postavi &kdiskfree; Ekran</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure &kdiskfree; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Postavi &kdiskfree; Ekran</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog has two tabbed windows, <guilabel>General Settings</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Mount Commands</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Ovaj dijalog ima dva tabovana prozora, <guilabel>Opšte Postavke</guilabel> i "
"<guilabel>Naredbe Montiranja</guilabel>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Opšte Postavke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the word <guilabel>visible</guilabel> or <guilabel>hidden</"
"guilabel> to turn display of an data field on or off."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na riječ <guilabel>vidljivo</guilabel> ili <guilabel>skriveno</"
"guilabel> da zaslon polja podataka upalite ili ugasite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the update frequency by editing the value. The value in the box is "
"the interval (in seconds) between updates of the &kdiskfree; display to "
"reflect the current status."
msgstr ""
"Promijenite učestalost ažuriranja promjenom vrijednosti. Vrijednost u boxu "
"je interval (u sekundama) među ažuriranjima &kdiskfree; zaslona da prikaže "
"trenutni status."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>File Manager</guilabel> setting controls the command executed "
"when the <guimenuitem>Open Filemanager</guimenuitem> popup menu item is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>File Manager</guilabel> postavka kontroliše naredbu koja se "
"izvršava kada je <guimenuitem>Otvori Filemanager</guimenuitem> popup meni "
"stavka odabrana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are also two check boxes. One controls if a file manager window will "
"be automatically opened when a device is mounted. The other causes an alert "
"window to pop up if a disk gets critically full."
msgstr ""
"Također, postoje dva check boxa. Jedan određuje da li će fajl menadžer "
"prozor biti automatski otvoren kada je uredjaj montiran. Drugi uzrokuje da "
"prozor za uzbunu iskoči ukoliko je disk skoro pun."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount Commands"
msgstr "Komande Montiranja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows the user to specify the mount and unmount commands for a given "
"device, as well as the icon used to represent it. More information on these "
"commands can be found on the man page for <application>mount</application> "
"(type <userinput><command>man</command> <option>mount</option></userinput> "
"at the command prompt)."
msgstr ""
"Dozvoljava korisniku da odredi naredbe montiranja i demontiranja za dati "
"uređaj, kao i ikonicu koja će ga predstavljati. Više informacija o ovim "
"naredbama možete pronaći ma man pageu za <application>mount</application> "
"(ukucajte <userinput><command>man</command> <option>mount</option></"
"userinput> u command promptu)."

